```{r load_library}
suppressWarnings(suppressMessages(library(swigex)))
```

```{r first display}
f1 = Fibo(50)
f1$display(FALSE)
```

```{r second display}
f2 = Fibo(100, "Test 100")
f2$display()
```

```{r third_display}
vec = fib(40)
print(vec)
```

```{r fourth_display}
vec = fib(40)
plot(seq(length(vec)), vec)
```
